<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0">
<title>三Agent思想辩论场</title>
<style>
:root {
  --bg: #faf7f2; --ink: #1a1714; --ink-dim: #8a8278;
  --card: #fffdf9; --border: #e8e3db; --shadow: 0 2px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
  --radius: 12px;
  --c1: #2d6a4f; --c2: #9b2226; --c3: #1e6091;
  --c4: #c9a96e; --c5: #6b5b4f;
  --font-body: 'Noto Serif SC', Georgia, serif;
  --font-ui: 'Noto Sans SC', system-ui, sans-serif;
}
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
body{
  background: var(--bg); color: var(--ink);
  font-family: var(--font-body); min-height: 100vh;
  display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;
  padding: 40px 20px;
}
.container{max-width: 800px; width: 100%}

/* Header */
.header{text-align: center; margin-bottom: 48px}
.header h1{font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.06em; margin-bottom: 8px}
.header .sub{font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--ink-dim)}
.header .characters{
  display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 24px; margin-top: 20px;
  font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--ink-dim);
}
.header .characters span{font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.04em}
.header .characters span:nth-child(1){color: var(--c1)}
.header .characters span:nth-child(2){color: var(--c2)}
.header .characters span:nth-child(3){color: var(--c3)}

/* Grid */
.grid{display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px}
@media(max-width:600px){.grid{grid-template-columns: 1fr}}

/* Card */
.card{
  background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 24px; box-shadow: var(--shadow);
  cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s; text-decoration: none; color: inherit;
  display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px;
}
.card:hover{transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.06)}
.card .badge{
  font-family: var(--font-ui); font-size: 0.6rem; letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  text-transform: uppercase; padding: 2px 10px; border-radius: 20px;
  display: inline-block; width: fit-content;
}
.card .title{font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 600}
.card .desc{font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--ink-dim); line-height: 1.6}

/* Variant colors */
.card.liquid .badge{background: rgba(0,113,227,0.08); color: #0071e3}
.card.river .badge{background: rgba(0,0,0,0.6); color: #c9a96e}
.card.epistolary .badge{background: rgba(45,106,79,0.08); color: var(--c1)}
.card.frost .badge{background: rgba(0,0,0,0.04); color: var(--ink-dim)}
.card.anime .badge{background: rgba(212,53,53,0.08); color: #d43535}

.card.liquid{border-top: 3px solid #0071e3}
.card.river{border-top: 3px solid var(--c4); background: #111}
.card.river .title{color: #ddd}.card.river .desc{color: #888}
.card.epistolary{border-top: 3px solid var(--c1)}
.card.frost{border-top: 3px solid var(--ink-dim)}
.card.anime{border-top: 3px solid #d43535}

/* Install hint */
.install-hint{
  text-align: center; margin-top: 40px; padding: 16px;
  background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: var(--radius); font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--ink-dim);
}

.footer{
  text-align: center; margin-top: 32px;
  font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--ink-dim);
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">

<header class="header">
  <h1>三Agent思想辩论场</h1>
  <p class="sub">庄周 · 尼采 · 波伏娃 — 跨越2400年的思想碰撞</p>
  <div class="characters">
    <span>庄周 · 道家</span>
    <span>尼采 · 权力意志</span>
    <span>波伏娃 · 存在主义</span>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="grid">

<a href="/pwa-liquid-glass.html" class="card liquid">
  <span class="badge">Liquid Glass</span>
  <span class="title">液态玻璃 · 臻境</span>
  <span class="desc">Apple 式连续曲率毛玻璃，四层深度折射，spring 动画曲线</span>
</a>

<a href="/pwa-river-of-light.html" class="card river">
  <span class="badge">Tenebrism</span>
  <span class="title">长河 · 光影</span>
  <span class="desc">伦勃朗照明·体积光·丁达尔效应，从绝对黑暗中浮现的思想</span>
</a>

<a href="/pwa-epistolary.html" class="card epistolary">
  <span class="badge">Epistolary</span>
  <span class="title">思想书简</span>
  <span class="desc">全屏聊天流，三种哲学书信气泡，私聊/群辩双模式</span>
</a>

<a href="/pwa-frost-white.html" class="card frost">
  <span class="badge">Minimalist</span>
  <span class="title">霜白 · 臻简</span>
  <span class="desc">Apple 式极简奢华，纳米阴影，毛玻璃悬浮卡片</span>
</a>

<a href="/pwa-anime-vn.html" class="card anime">
  <span class="badge">Visual Novel</span>
  <span class="title">次元 · 绘卷</span>
  <span class="desc">视觉小说竖屏，角色立绘/集中线/网点/水晶章节</span>
</a>

</div>

<div class="install-hint">
  <strong>添加到主屏幕：</strong> 打开任意一款 → 浏览器菜单 → "添加到主屏幕" → 像 App 一样使用
</div>

<footer class="footer">
  Powered by DeepSeek · Debate Engine v3 · Railway
</footer>

</div>
</body>
</html>
